	<span>PHYSICIANS CHOICE MANAGEMENT, LLC OPENS NEW CENTER:</span>
	
<p>	<strong>Gadsden, Alabama, November 17, 2011.</strong>  Physicians Choice Management, LLC announces the opening effective today of a new state of the art dialysis center certified by Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services and the State of Alabama to dialyze End Stage Renal Disease Patients.  The Gadsden dialysis center located at 800 Goodyear Avenue, Gadsden Alabama offers among other modalities Hemodialysis, Home Dialysis, and Peritoneal dialysis and is comprised of a maximum 21 hemodialysis stations with an initial 10 stations with a total capacity for 120 hemodialysis patients.  Attending Physicians include Doctors Venugopala Bheemanathini, Gary Kwan, Edward Hwang, Mohammed Kabir, David Zinn and Prathyusha Maddela.
</p>
